mutation ($payload:BplusItSappiCreateModuleInput!)
{
	bplusItSappiCreateModule (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		systemId
		systemName
		channelId
		channelParty
		channelComponent
		channelName
		flowParty
		flowComponent
		flowInterfaceName
		flowInterfaceNamespace
		parameterGroup
		name
		parameterName
		parameterValue
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
